					<![CDATA[
						 <p>Short, sweet, and to-the-point without feeling rushed. It embodies what a scip should be, in my eyes: a snippet of a window into an absurd and illogical world, where things make sense only when you don't look too hard. It's this kind of stuff that makes me want another Short Works contest, and that's something upvote-worthy in my eyes. +1</p> 
				 	]]>
