					<![CDATA[
						 <p>Here we go again.</p> <p>Pic is from <a href="https://commons.wikimedia.org/wiki/File:Donini_dry_cleaning_machines_(Bologna)_3.jpg">here</a>.</p> <div class="collapsible-block"> <div class="collapsible-block-folded"><a class="collapsible-block-link" href="javascript:;">I'd&nbsp;like&nbsp;to&nbsp;thank</a></div> <div class="collapsible-block-unfolded" style="display:none"> <div class="collapsible-block-unfolded-link"><a class="collapsible-block-link" href="javascript:;">my&nbsp;stomach</a></div> <div class="collapsible-block-content"> <p><span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/drbleep" ><img class="small" src="http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=2887044&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1516343217" alt="DrBleep" style="background-image:url(http://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=2887044)" /></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/drbleep" >DrBleep</a></span> - for graciously checking and correcting my more egregious science violations</p> <p>Ryan North - for writing <a href="http://qwantz.com/index.php?comic=1455">this comic</a> whose last panel partially inspired this skip</p> <p>Whichever person in chat who brought up &quot;meat-eating bacteria&quot;, leading me to consider &quot;meat, eating bacteria&quot; and subsequently &quot;people, eating bacteria&quot;</p> <p><span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/the-great-hippo" ><img class="small" src="http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=3122708&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1516343217" alt="The Great Hippo" style="background-image:url(http://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=3122708)" /></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/the-great-hippo" >The Great Hippo</a></span> - for brainstorming assistance</p> <p><span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/9volt" ><img class="small" src="http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=2800867&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1516343217" alt="9Volt" style="background-image:url(http://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=2800867)" /></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/9volt" >9Volt</a></span>, <span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/moklin" ><img class="small" src="http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=3009732&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1516343217" alt="Moklin" style="background-image:url(http://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=3009732)" /></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/moklin" >Moklin</a></span>, <span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/sunnyclockwork" ><img class="small" src="http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=1621343&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1516343217" alt="SunnyClockwork" style="background-image:url(http://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=1621343)" /></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/sunnyclockwork" >SunnyClockwork</a></span> - for reading the drafts</p> </div> </div> </div> 
